    createCharacter(){

    }
}

Apollo client:
--------------
- Encapsulates HTTP logic used to interact with a GraphQL API
- Doubles as  a client side state mgmt alternative.
- If your graphql api is also an apollo server, provides some extra features.
- It is framework independent
- Offers plug apporach for extending capabilities